* SQL Warehouse\nPerformance
** Access Path
***_ SQL warehouse
***_ Monitoring tab
** Live Statistics
***_ Warehouse status
***_ Running queries
***_ Queued queries
***_ Current cluster count
** Peak Query Count Chart
***_ Max concurrent queries
***_ Running + queued
***_ Demand spikes visible
** Running Clusters Chart
***_ Cluster allocation over time
***_ Shows autoscaling behavior
***_ Max capacity sustained = undersized
** Query History Table
***_ Start time, duration, user
***_ Filter long-running queries
***_ Identify resource consumers
@endmindmap
